# Override global gitignore (tracked in this repo)
!.claude
!.claudeignore
!CLAUDE.md

# Claude Code local settings
.claude/settings.local.json

# Skills under .claude/skills/ default to ignored. Publishable skills live in
# rysk-tanaka/skills and are placed as symlinks by `mise run setup-skills`.
# Pristine external skills (catalog.json source = owner/repo, no local edits)
# are restored by the same task via `gh skill install`, so their bodies stay
# ignored. Customized external skills (e.g. empirical-prompt-tuning carries a
# local SKILL-ja.md and tracks a drifted upstream) stay re-included below.
# Re-include the metadata files and environment-dependent skills tracked here.
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/.markdownlint-cli2.jsonc
!.claude/skills/catalog.json
!.claude/skills/claude-process/
!.claude/skills/empirical-prompt-tuning/
!.claude/skills/read-screen/
!.claude/skills/setup-workflows/
!.claude/skills/sync-brew/
